&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Global Institute for Shaping a Better Future&lt;/strong&gt; is a global learning engine connecting educators, system leaders, and others changemakers at the forefront of reshaping education. The Institute contributes to the learning and leadership development of those working to transform education within and beyond the Teach For All network, also generating new insights, evidence, and tools to accelerate progress across the field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will help launch new leadership initiatives and scale successful efforts globally, including across the Asia-Pacific region. This role offers the opportunity to help shape how leadership is developed across one of the world’s largest networks of changemakers working to reshape education.&lt;/p&gt;
