&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coaching senior leaders&lt;/strong&gt; in peer learning groups to deepen leadership practice and collective impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contributing to a pioneering set of programs &lt;/strong&gt;that develop inner leadership for system change among individuals and teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Co-designing and facilitating workshops&lt;/strong&gt; through the Global Institute for Shaping a Better Future to grow the leadership of thousands of educators and system leaders worldwide&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
